    "body": "If anyone else wanted a solution to this, you can use a custom module as a temporary solution:\r\n\r\n```toml\r\nformat = \"\"\"\r\n$git_branch\\\r\n${custom.git_status}\"\"\"\r\n\r\n[custom.git_status]\r\nwhen = \"\"\" [[ $(git status -s) != '' ]] \"\"\" \r\nformat = \" [!](red)\"\r\n```",
